title.narrative: Support to National Malaria Programme - Procurement of Goods

description.narrative: This activity (Support to National Malaria Programme - Procurement of Goods) is a component of Support to National Malaria Programme, Nigeria reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £28,581,346. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Malaria control. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-08-2008 and the end date is 30-06-2016.
